background = ExtResource("1_eti65")
lines = Array[String](["Long before the Iron Cities cast their shadows upon the world, the Mages lived in harmony with the Stars—celestial guardians who watched over the land, sea, and sky.

Through sacred voices they wove their magic, and beneath the blessings of the Stars, the world flourished.", "Yet the hearts of men grew restless.

They raised cities of iron where sacred forests once stood, and forged engines whose thunder drowned the whispers of the old world.

Thus did ambition eclipse reverence, and the ancient bond between mankind, nature, and the Stars began to fade.", "Then came the hunters of the Iron Cities.

Fearing the power they could neither command nor understand, they pursued the Mage clans without mercy.

Voices were stolen. Songs of magic fell silent.

And one by one, the Stars vanished from the heavens.

Some believed they had abandoned the Mages.

Others whispered they had joined the Iron Cities.

None knew the truth.", "Yet among the fallen remained one.

A child born without a voice.

While every other Mage called upon magic through song, the child could only watch in silence, believing their silence to be a curse.

Yet somehow... their hands answered where their voice could not.", "The elders called it the Silent Blessing.

An ancient tale spoke of those who could weave magic not through voice... but through hand.

Most believed it was nothing more than an old legend.

Until the day every other Mage lost their voice...

...and only one remained.", "Whether the Stars truly forsook the world... or whether another truth lies hidden... no one can say.

But the voices of the Mages remain lost, and strange powers now stir within the machines of the Iron Cities.

Go forth, Child of the Silent Blessing.

Seek the truth behind the silence...

...and let the Stars guide your path."])
bgm_to_play = ExtResource("2_6rhc6")
